  "description" : "Thousands of years ago in the Fairy Realm of Ye Luoli, Prince Jin and Princess Luo Li met by chance. One believed in power, the other in love; gold and true feelings drew them closer under the pull of fate. However, Mandora`s greed and schemes relentlessly pressed in, and gold, power, and love intertwined into an inescapable destiny. With the royal family on the verge of collapse and a storm brewing, this encounter, which began with a spark of attraction, would ultimately become the prologue to rewriting the fate of the Fairy Realm. Could they hold onto each other in the face of despair?\nsource: bgm.tv\\googletranslate",
